         "import { Component, h, State, Prop } from '@stencil/core';\nimport { LimeWebComponentPlatform } from '@limetech/lime-web-components';\n\n@Component({\n    tag: 'layout-login',\n    shadow: true,\n    styleUrl: 'layout-login.scss',\n})\nexport class LayoutLogin {\n    @Prop() public platform: LimeWebComponentPlatform;\n    @State() isSignup: boolean = false;\n\n    constructor() {\n        this.toggleSignupContainer = this.toggleSignupContainer.bind(this);\n    }\n\n    public render() {\n        const loginClass = this.isSignup\n            ?
